The app stores transactions in SQLite and has four main tabs: Dashboard, Transactions, Add Transaction, and Analytics.

3
00:01:10,000 --> 00:02:30,000
Now I’ll add a sample expense. Select a date, pick Type as Expense, choose a category, enter the amount, add a short description, and click Add Transaction.

4
00:02:30,000 --> 00:03:20,000
