5
00:03:20,000 --> 00:04:20,000
In Transactions, you can filter by type and delete records. Select a row and click Delete Selected to remove it.

6
00:04:20,000 --> 00:05:20,000
Open Analytics to view Income vs Expense, Category Breakdown, and Monthly Trend charts. Axis labels and values use Indian Rupees.

